column1: Uchi////I wish I could tell you the name of all 10 dishes we had
column2: but they came out so fast I couldn't keep up. They did pace the dishes well
column3: but as soon as we finished one
column4: another one was already appearing. The staff was awesome and for every dish they told us specifically what it was and how it was prepared. I did love that. They were all attentive and helpful.
